flowchart TD
  E[Stable HTTP/code/requestId] --> A{Auth 401?}
  A -->|yes| R[Re-authenticate once]
  A -->|no| P{Permission/ban 403?}
  P -->|yes| U[Show safe access state; do not retry blindly]
  P -->|no| C{Conflict 409?}
  C -->|yes| S[Resync authoritative revision/epoch]
  C -->|no| L{Rate 429?}
  L -->|yes| B[Respect Retry-After/backoff]
  L -->|no| T{Temporary 5xx?}
  T -->|yes| O[Bounded retry + operator evidence]
  T -->|no| V[Correct request/input]
  O --> G[Log code + requestId, never secrets]
